transcript.text: Hello welcome to on print shop.
This video is about image binding with additional option attribute and additional options in a single row under additional option group.
We will discuss 2 updates in this video together.
First image binding with additional option attribute.
Second multiple additional option in single row under additional option group.
Here T-shirt images are bounded with colors.
If you select green, green color image will display.
If you select black it will show black T-shirt image.
Here size is additional option group and all sizes XSSML and XLR separate additional options which are visible in single row.
Let's see how we can configure both the settings in admin.
For image binding we need to go to gallery click on Image gallery setting.
Here you can bind only one additional option with image gallery.
While uploading image you can bind it with specific attribute.
Here you can see all four images are bounded with specific color.
Now we will see how multiple additional option can set in a single row under additional option group.
Here you can see multiple additional options available like XSSML and XL.
Now click on additional option group.
Here is setting available option display style.
Set it as inline and also you can configure a number of option in a row.
Thank you.
If you have any queries please contact us at support at onprintshop com.

. Fixed Quantity and Price : allows you to define fix price for fixed quantity of product e.g. for 100
In case of Advanced CMYK color palette, colors in print ready file may differ from shown in designer studio.
. Range based with multiplication : in this different quantity ranges are available with different prices.
Total Price = Quantity * price. e.g for 10 quantity consider range 1-200 price = 20 so total price = 10*
. Range based without multiplication : in this different quantity ranges are available with different
prices. e.g for 10 quantity consider range 1-200 price = 20 so total price = 20
. Size based Price (Dynamic Size) : Customer will get option for enter custom width & height at front
side. System will calculate pricing based on area.
